OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome clear
OL,6,Fperiods in the east at first, but
OL,7,Fcloudier conditions in the west will
OL,8,Fedge eastwards overnight, perhaps
OL,9,Fgiving the odd spot of rain. The
OL,10,Fbreeze increasing, especially across
OL,11,Fthe Derbyshire hills. Mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FMostly dry start with
OL,14,Fvariable, often cloudy conditions.
OL,15,FCloud thickening from the west in the
OL,16,Fafternoon bringing outbreaks of rain
OL,17,Ffor most, heaviest rain across the
OL,18,FPeak District. Mild, breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
