OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday,
OL,6,Frain some heavy, clearing later.
OL,7,FOccasionally strong winds. Saturday
OL,8,Fmostly dry, some bright spells and
OL,9,Flighter winds. Sunday, rain mainly
OL,10,Facross the Peak District, drier
OL,11,Felsewhere. Windy but mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
